  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Short term hip function</measure>
    <time_frame>within six weeks post-operative</time_frame>
    <description>Early functional outcome will be measured using the modified Harris Hip score at the first post-operative visit</description>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Short-Term Pain Levels of direct anterior and anterolateral surgical approaches</measure>
    <description>Short-term (6 weeks post-op) pain will also be compared between the approach used for the total hip replacement: namely direct anterior and anterolateral using a VAS pain scale</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
